#4-40 screws, each with a length of 3/16th inch. You can also use a 1/4 inch-long screw if you place a small washer between it and the top of the circuit board.

Sources

Navx documentation recommends those screws for mounting their gyro, and you have a similar ask of mounting a circuit board to the MXP mounting holes on the roborio.

The REV digital MXP display comes with those sized bolts and its the same use case.
